							_type: 'model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.TextBlockElement',
							html: '<p>Is he trying to reduce screen time? Lauren Gould, the Filter’s editorial coordinator, swears by the <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/thefilter-us/2026/jan/30/papier-reading-journal">Papier Wonder Reading Journal</a> that “encouraged me to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/thefilter-us/2025/nov/03/best-meditation-apps#best-meditation-app-for-beginners-headspace-meditation-health">implement mindfulness</a> into each reading session – and in turn, my everyday routine”. Coupled with prompts such as “First impressions?” and “Would you read this book again?,” this reading journal is the screen-free gift he never knew he needed. Get 15% off all Papier stationery from 8 to 21 June.</p>',
