							html: '<p>Karen Yuan, the Filter’s commissioning editor, calls Baked By Melissa’s treats “reliably <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/thefilter-us/2026/feb/10/best-valentines-day-food-gifts#baked-by-melissa-mini-cupcakes-box">giftable cupcakes</a> with its signature cutesy looks”. Treat dad to a 50-pack of cupcakes with 18 flavors such as cookie butter brownie and triple chocolate fudge, all wrapped in a limited-edition “Happy Father’s Day” sleeve. From 7 to 21 June, get $10 off all 50 packs with code TREATDAD, and take advantage of next-day deliveries when you order by 2pm ET.</p>',
