							html: '<p>If his nickname is Mr Fix It, here’s a deal on a DeWalt power tool kit for 39% off. In Filter contributor Tim Stevens’s list of best <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/thefilter-us/2025/dec/13/best-gifts-for-diyers">gifts for the DIYers</a>, he bills the cordless drill as an essential tool. “A cordless drill is an absolute necessity for everything from making holes to driving screws,” he says. “But gifting one is something of a commitment: you’re not just giving a drill, you’re granting access to an entire battery-powered ecosystem. DeWalt is a perfect choice.” It is available in this set on sale.</p>',
